<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="in-the-sbs-way">in the / sb's way</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>挡某人的道；妨碍某人：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Nothing is to stand in my way. 
没有什么能阻挡我。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Although I thought I was helping my parents prepare dinner, I was only in the way. 
虽然我认为自己是在帮父母准备饭菜，但实际上只是碍手碍脚。</p></div></div>